item.title: Readme
item.description: Welcome to the SRC folder for the Gohugo Ananke Theme. The contents of this folder are used to generate CSS and javascript. You may never have to touch anything here, unless you want to more deeply customize your styles. Tools Yarn We use Yarn for package managment (instead of NPM) because it’s fast and generates a lock file to make dependency management more consistent. The theme’s .gitignore file should be kept intact to make sure that all files in the node_modules folder are not pushed to the repository.
